lead_paragraph: QUINN--Cecilia Ann, (85), on June 17, 2016 of Garden City, NY. Beloved wife of the late James J. Quinn. Loving mother of Maureen, Matthew, Eileen, Patricia, and the late Catherine. Cherished grandma of Samantha, Emily, Erin, Spencer, Max, and Liam. Visitation Wednesday 2-4 and 7-9pm at Fairchild Sons Funeral Home, Inc., 1201 Franklin Avenue, Garden City, NY. Mass Thursday 10am at St. Joseph's R.C. Church, Garden City, NY. Interment to follow at Holy Rood Cemetery, Westbury, NY. In lieu of flowers, donations may be made to: the Alzheimer's Foundation of America. 1/3
